{"word":"G190 - ἀκολουθέω - akolouthéō - ak-ol-oo-theh'-o - Follow","slug":"G190","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκολουθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>akolouthéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ak-ol-oo-theh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Follow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - akoloutheo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ak-ol-oo-theh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a particle of union) and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>keleuthos</b> (a <i>road</i>); properly to <i>be in the same way with</i>, that is, to <i>accompany</i> (specifically as a disciple): - follow, reach."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1811\">G1811</a>, <a href=\"#/G1872\">G1872</a>, <a href=\"#/G3877\">G3877</a>, <a href=\"#/G4870\">G4870</a>"}]}